  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 41-3-65, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO AUTHORIZE THE STATE DEPARTMENT OF HEALTH TO INCREASE FOOD ESTABLISHMENT ANNUAL PERMIT FEES, PRIVATE WATER SUPPLY APPROVAL FEES, AND ONSITE WASTEWATER PROGRAM FEES BY A CERTAIN PERCENTAGE DURING THE NEXT THREE FISCAL YEARS UP TO A MAXIMUM AMOUNT; TO AMEND SECTIONS 41-3-18, 41-67-12 AND 41-67-25, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO CONFORM TO THE PRECEDING PROVISIONS; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
